---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
---
<Layout>
    <Header></Header>
      <div>
        <div class="detailProduct">
            <div>
                <img src={"/poncho.jpg"} alt="" />
                <p>{"$100"}</p>
                <p>{"Poncho"}</p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Fugit nesciunt earum similique cumque illum commodi doloribus, repellendus ipsum, possimus placeat necessitatibus soluta obcaecati culpa minus neque odio nihil, provident voluptates.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/cart" style="text-decoration: none; color: #523B2B; width: 100%;"><button>Add to Cart</button></a>
